text: Bangalaia margaretae is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by E. Forrest Gilmour in 1956. It is known from Mozambique.BioLib.cz - Bangalaia margaretae. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Prosopocerini Category:Beetles described in 1956
title: Bangalaia margaretae
